<p><strong>Cucumber Watermelon Salad</strong> &mdash; &#129367;&#127817;&#129362; An EASY salad with watermelon, cucumber, arugula, goat cheese, candied nuts, and drizzled with a homemade balsamic glaze! A PERFECT summer salad for those days when it&rsquo;s too hot to cook!</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="650" height="975" data-pin-url="https://www.averiecooks.com/balsamic-watermelon-and-cucumber-salad/?tp_image_id=77712" data-pin-title="Balsamic Watermelon and Cucumber Salad" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20650%20975'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Balsamic Watermelon Cucumber Salad &mdash; An EASY, healthy, and light salad with watermelon, cucumber, arugula, goat cheese, candied nuts, and drizzled with a homemade balsamic glaze!! A PERFECT summer salad for those days when it's too hot to cook!!" class="wp-image-77712" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/watermelonsalad-5.jpg 650w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/watermelonsalad-5-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/watermelonsalad-5-240x360.jpg 240w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/watermelonsalad-5-480x720.jpg 480w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/watermelonsalad-5-280x420.jpg 280w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/watermelonsalad-5-560x840.jpg 560w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/watermelonsalad-5-360x540.jpg 360w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px" data-lazy-src="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/watermelonsalad-5.jpg" /><noscript><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="650" height="975" data-pin-url="https://www.averiecooks.com/balsamic-watermelon-and-cucumber-salad/?tp_image_id=77712" data-pin-title="Balsamic Watermelon and Cucumber Salad" src="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/watermelonsalad-5.jpg" alt="Balsamic Watermelon Cucumber Salad &mdash; An EASY, healthy, and light salad with watermelon, cucumber, arugula, goat cheese, candied nuts, and drizzled with a homemade balsamic glaze!! A PERFECT summer salad for those days when it's too hot to cook!!" class="wp-image-77712" srcset="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/watermelonsalad-5.jpg 650w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/watermelonsalad-5-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/watermelonsalad-5-240x360.jpg 240w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/watermelonsalad-5-480x720.jpg 480w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/watermelonsalad-5-280x420.jpg 280w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/watermelonsalad-5-560x840.jpg 560w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/watermelonsalad-5-360x540.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px" /></noscript></figure>
