<div class="block-tip cwp-large"><div class="block-tip__inner">

<h2 class="wp-block-heading block-tip__title" id="h-storage-instructions">Storage Instructions</h2>



<p><strong>Salad: </strong>Is best eaten immediately and can&rsquo;t be assembled in advance. </p>



<p><strong>Balsamic glaze: </strong>You will have lots of balsamic reduction leftover, and it will keep for weeks in an airtight container in the fridge. As long as you&rsquo;re going to the trouble to make it, you may as well have extra for future recipes, because it&rsquo;s great drizzled over chicken, salmon, etc.</p>

</div></div>

<div id="recipe"></div><div id="wprm-recipe-container-75024" class="wprm-recipe-container" data-recipe-id="75024" data-servings="2"><div class="wprm-recipe wprm-recipe-template-cwp-food"><div class="cwp-food-header">
	<div class="cwp-food-header__right">
