<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-more-summer-salad-recipes-nbsp">More Summer Salad Recipes:&nbsp;</h2>



<p><a href="https://www.averiecooks.com/chicken-chopped-salad/" data-wpel-link="internal" target="_self"><span data-sheets-value="{" chopped salad data-sheets-userformat="{">Chopped Chicken Salad</span></a> &mdash; An EASY chopped salad with so much FLAVOR and CRUNCH topped with PERFECT juicy oven-baked chicken that&rsquo;s ready in 15 minutes!! Homemade honey apple cider vinaigrette adds the finishing touch!!</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter"><img decoding="async" width="650" height="975" data-pin-url="https://www.averiecooks.com/balsamic-watermelon-and-cucumber-salad/?tp_image_id=77769" data-pin-title="Balsamic Watermelon and Cucumber Salad" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20650%20975'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Grilled chicken breast slices on a fresh garden salad with avocado, tomatoes, cucumbers, and croutons." class="wp-image-77769" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/choppedsalad-4.jpg 650w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/choppedsalad-4-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/choppedsalad-4-240x360.jpg 240w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/choppedsalad-4-480x720.jpg 480w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/choppedsalad-4-280x420.jpg 280w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/choppedsalad-4-560x840.jpg 560w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/choppedsalad-4-360x540.jpg 360w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px" data-lazy-src="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/choppedsalad-4.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="650" height="975" data-pin-url="https://www.averiecooks.com/balsamic-watermelon-and-cucumber-salad/?tp_image_id=77769" data-pin-title="Balsamic Watermelon and Cucumber Salad" src="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/choppedsalad-4.jpg" alt="Grilled chicken breast slices on a fresh garden salad with avocado, tomatoes, cucumbers, and croutons." class="wp-image-77769" srcset="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/choppedsalad-4.jpg 650w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/choppedsalad-4-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/choppedsalad-4-240x360.jpg 240w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/choppedsalad-4-480x720.jpg 480w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/choppedsalad-4-280x420.jpg 280w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/choppedsalad-4-560x840.jpg 560w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/choppedsalad-4-360x540.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px" /></noscript></figure>



<p><a href="https://www.averiecooks.com/southwest-chicken-cobb-salad/" data-wpel-link="internal" target="_self">Southwest Chicken Cobb Salad</a> &ndash; &#129367;&#129472;&#127813;&#127805; A Southwestern spin on traditional Cobb salad complete with tender chicken, crispy bacon, cheese, hard-boiled eggs, tomatoes, black beans, corn, and avocado over a bed of Romaine lettuce!&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" data-pin-url="https://www.averiecooks.com/balsamic-watermelon-and-cucumber-salad/?tp_image_id=118704" data-pin-title="Balsamic Watermelon and Cucumber Salad" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%201800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-118704" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40.png 1200w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40-800x1200.png 800w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40-240x360.png 240w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40-768x1152.png 768w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40-1024x1536.png 1024w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40-400x600.png 400w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40-600x900.png 600w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40-150x225.png 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" data-lazy-src="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40.png" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" data-pin-url="https://www.averiecooks.com/balsamic-watermelon-and-cucumber-salad/?tp_image_id=118704" data-pin-title="Balsamic Watermelon and Cucumber Salad" src="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118704" srcset="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40.png 1200w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40-800x1200.png 800w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40-240x360.png 240w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40-768x1152.png 768w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40-1024x1536.png 1024w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40-400x600.png 400w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40-600x900.png 600w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-40-150x225.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></noscript></figure>



<p><a href="https://www.averiecooks.com/layered-beef-taco-salad/" data-wpel-link="internal" target="_self">Layered Taco Salad</a>&nbsp;&mdash; A classic taco salad that everyone LOVES, it&rsquo;s EASY, and it&rsquo;s ready in 20 minutes!! There&rsquo;s ground beef, refried beans, red peppers, tortilla chips, cheese, lettuce, and tomatoes!!&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="650" height="975" data-pin-url="https://www.averiecooks.com/balsamic-watermelon-and-cucumber-salad/?tp_image_id=118705" data-pin-title="Balsamic Watermelon and Cucumber Salad" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20650%20975'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-118705" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-41.png 650w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-41-240x360.png 240w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-41-400x600.png 400w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-41-600x900.png 600w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-41-150x225.png 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px" data-lazy-src="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-41.png" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="650" height="975" data-pin-url="https://www.averiecooks.com/balsamic-watermelon-and-cucumber-salad/?tp_image_id=118705" data-pin-title="Balsamic Watermelon and Cucumber Salad" src="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-41.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118705" srcset="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-41.png 650w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-41-240x360.png 240w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-41-400x600.png 400w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-41-600x900.png 600w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-41-150x225.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px" /></noscript></figure>



<p><a href="https://www.averiecooks.com/mediterranean-cobb-salad/" data-wpel-link="internal" target="_self">Mediterranean Salad</a> &mdash; This M<span data-sheets-value="{" salad data-sheets-userformat="{">editerranean salad</span>&nbsp;easy, healthy, accidentally vegetarian, ready in 10 minutes, and you can easily size the recipe up if you&rsquo;re making it for a larger group.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter"><img width="650" height="975" decoding="async" data-pin-url="https://www.averiecooks.com/balsamic-watermelon-and-cucumber-salad/?tp_image_id=59038" data-pin-title="Balsamic Watermelon and Cucumber Salad" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20650%20975'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="A colorful mediterranean salad with artichokes, boiled eggs, olives, sun-dried tomatoes, cucumber, and feta cheese." class="wp-image-59038" data-lazy-src="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/mediterraneancobb-650x975.jpg"><noscript><img width="650" height="975" decoding="async" data-pin-url="https://www.averiecooks.com/balsamic-watermelon-and-cucumber-salad/?tp_image_id=59038" data-pin-title="Balsamic Watermelon and Cucumber Salad" src="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/mediterraneancobb-650x975.jpg" alt="A colorful mediterranean salad with artichokes, boiled eggs, olives, sun-dried tomatoes, cucumber, and feta cheese." class="wp-image-59038"></noscript></figure>



<p><a href="https://www.averiecooks.com/strawberry-pecan-grilled-chicken-salad-pecan-butter-vinaigrette/" data-wpel-link="internal" target="_self"><span data-sheets-value="{" pecan grilled chicken salad data-sheets-userformat="{">Strawberry Chicken Salad</span></a> &mdash; The grilled chicken is so JUICY and moist thanks to a homemade pecan butter marinade!! Sweet strawberries and crunchy pecans add extra texture and FLAVOR!!</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter"><img width="650" height="975" decoding="async" data-pin-url="https://www.averiecooks.com/balsamic-watermelon-and-cucumber-salad/?tp_image_id=59261" data-pin-title="Balsamic Watermelon and Cucumber Salad" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20650%20975'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Grilled chicken salad with strawberries and pecans, served with a vinaigrette dressing." class="wp-image-59261" data-lazy-src="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/pecanchicken-4-650x975.jpg"><noscript><img width="650" height="975" decoding="async" data-pin-url="https://www.averiecooks.com/balsamic-watermelon-and-cucumber-salad/?tp_image_id=59261" data-pin-title="Balsamic Watermelon and Cucumber Salad" src="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/pecanchicken-4-650x975.jpg" alt="Grilled chicken salad with strawberries and pecans, served with a vinaigrette dressing." class="wp-image-59261"></noscript></figure>



<p><a href="https://www.averiecooks.com/greek-pita-chip-salad/" data-wpel-link="internal" target="_self"><span data-sheets-value="{" pita chip salad data-sheets-userformat="{">Greek Pita Chip Salad</span></a> &mdash; Greek salad just got a makeover!! Still uses classic ingredients like red peppers, cucumbers, onions, olives, and feta but now there are PITA CHIPS for extra crunch and texture!&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter"><img width="650" height="975" decoding="async" data-pin-url="https://www.averiecooks.com/balsamic-watermelon-and-cucumber-salad/?tp_image_id=58894" data-pin-title="Balsamic Watermelon and Cucumber Salad" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20650%20975'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="A bowl of fresh fattoush salad with vegetables, herbs, and toasted bread pieces." class="wp-image-58894" data-lazy-src="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/greekpitachipsalad-7-650x975.jpg"><noscript><img width="650" height="975" decoding="async" data-pin-url="https://www.averiecooks.com/balsamic-watermelon-and-cucumber-salad/?tp_image_id=58894" data-pin-title="Balsamic Watermelon and Cucumber Salad" src="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/greekpitachipsalad-7-650x975.jpg" alt="A bowl of fresh fattoush salad with vegetables, herbs, and toasted bread pieces." class="wp-image-58894"></noscript></figure>



<p><a href="https://www.averiecooks.com/pesto-chicken-caprese-salad/" data-wpel-link="internal" target="_self">Pesto Chicken Caprese Salad</a>&nbsp;&mdash; Homemade pesto coats every bite of JUICY chicken, tomatoes, and fresh mozzarella in this fun twist on caprese salad!! EASY, ready in 20 minutes, and loaded with rich basil flavor!!</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="650" height="975" data-pin-url="https://www.averiecooks.com/balsamic-watermelon-and-cucumber-salad/?tp_image_id=118706" data-pin-title="Balsamic Watermelon and Cucumber Salad" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20650%20975'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-118706" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-42.png 650w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-42-240x360.png 240w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-42-400x600.png 400w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-42-600x900.png 600w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-42-150x225.png 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px" data-lazy-src="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-42.png" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="650" height="975" data-pin-url="https://www.averiecooks.com/balsamic-watermelon-and-cucumber-salad/?tp_image_id=118706" data-pin-title="Balsamic Watermelon and Cucumber Salad" src="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-42.png" alt="" class="wp-image-118706" srcset="https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-42.png 650w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-42-240x360.png 240w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-42-400x600.png 400w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-42-600x900.png 600w, https://www.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image-42-150x225.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px" /></noscript></figure>

